Package org.jivesoftware.openfire.vcard

Interface Summary
VCardListener Interface to listen for vCard changes.
VCardProvider Provider interface for users vcards.
 

Class Summary
DefaultVCardProvider Default implementation of the VCardProvider interface, which reads and writes data from the ofVCard database table.
VCardEventDispatcher Dispatches vCard events.
VCardManager Manages VCard information for users.
